simple adaptor for getting tally signals into a jvc camera.
Tally-System must be set to 'Studio' in the camera settings.
cable-info in the above directory.

instead of the optocopler an LDR can be used for grabbing signals from
other tally-lamps (ex.: BMD Camera Converter)

Hardware and Software is in early prototype state.
(Works most of the time; but encountering deadlocks on rare occasions)
